0) Install OS
1) Install Python
2) Install pip & Install virtualenv (Package)
    $ pip install virtualenv
3) Create Environment(virtualenv .env)
    $ virtualenv .env
4) Activate Environment(.env\Scripts\activate)
    $ .env\scripts\activate
5) Install Packages in activated Environment
    $ pip install flask
6) Write/Clone Source Code
    $ app.py
7) Run app.py file
    $ python app.py
    $ flask run